  UpgradeType: 1
  WeaponType: 1
  DamageType: 3
  UpgradeName: Magnetic Field
  UpgradeDescription:
  - Create a magnetic orb field that rotates around the player for a duration, dealing
    damage and knockback enemies.
  - Increase orbs piercing by 1 and duration by 1s
  - Increase orbs size by 30% and duration by 1s
  - Increase knockback by 50% and damage by 25%
  - Increase orbs piercing by 2 and increase total numbers of orbs by 2 (Max 6)
  - Orbs now remain infinite
  MaxLevel: 6
  ID: 3
